EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 0900Z TO 1900Z DAILY
   10 THRU 15 JUL WITHIN 20 MILES OF:
   A. 57-16N 008-05W.
   B. 57-30N 008-31W.
   VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER AREA SHOULD CONTACT
   HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON VHF CH 16 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 152000Z JUL.
